# Components & Architecture

- **UI Library:** Always prioritize using **shadcn/ui** components. Check `src/components/ui/` before creating custom elements.
- **Features:** Domain UI and data live in `src/features/<domain>/` with thin route files in `src/app/`. Use `components/[Name]/` only for app-wide or design-system-level pieces outside a single domain.
- **Complexity:** If a component exceeds 150 lines, extract sub-components within the same directory.
- **Typing:** Use `interface` for Props. Always export: `export interface [Name]Props`.
- **Server First:** Use Server Components by default. Add `'use client'` ONLY for hooks (useState, useEffect) or event listeners.

